<li id="cite_note-canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html-9">^ <a href="#cite_ref-canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html_9-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html_9-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFLindzen2004">Lindzen, Richard S. (February 23,2004). <a href="http://meteo.lcd.lu/globalwarming/Lindzen/canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html" class="external text" title="http://meteo.lcd.lu/globalwarming/Lindzen/canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html" rel="nofollow">"Canadian Reactions To Sir David King"</a>. <a href="/wiki/The_Hill_Times" title="The Hill Times">The Hill Times</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://meteo.lcd.lu/globalwarming/Lindzen/canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html" class="external free" title="http://meteo.lcd.lu/globalwarming/Lindzen/canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html" rel="nofollow">http://meteo.lcd.lu/globalwarming/Lindzen/canadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-04-05</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Canadian+Reactions+To+Sir+David+King&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Lindzen&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+S.&amp;rft.au=Lindzen%2C+Richard+S.&amp;rft.date=February+23%2C2004&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BThe+Hill+Times%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmeteo.lcd.lu%2Fglobalwarming%2FLindzen%2Fcanadian_reactions_to_sir_david_king.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Richard_Lindzen"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
